market_opportunities.nostalgia_content: Old franchises and nostalgic content are seeing renewed interest. Consider creating content that taps into childhood shows or classic movie themes.
market_opportunities.interactive_gaming: Interactive and community-driven gaming content is underrepresented but shows promise. Explore opportunities in gamification and community-focused streams.
